Ngwenda Gold Says its Board Was Altered Fraudulently, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-02-22T05:15:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-22/ngwenda-gold-says-its-board-was-altered-fraudulently-business-day-reports.html
Ngwenda Gold has had its board of
directors fraudulently replaced at  South Africa ’s company
registry, Johannesburg’s Business Day reported, citing court
papers.  Last year Kalahari Resources, a manganese miner, won a
court battle to have its directors reinstated after a similar
incident.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  